      • exampleBaseClass

        public abstract String exampleBaseClass
        This adds a {code @include.example exampleBaseClass#updateActionTestName()} javadoc tag to all generated update actions.

        Where <i>updateActionTestName</i> is derived by un-capitalizing the update action name (e.g. for a SetKey update action the updateActionTestName is setKey.

        This follows our convention to have integration tests for all of our update actions.

        Returns:
        the example base class name
        Default:
        ""

      • generateDefaultFactory

        public abstract boolean generateDefaultFactory
        Specifies whether there should be a default factory method generated. a default factory method accepts all required parameters as argument.
        Returns:
        true if you need to generate a default factory, false otherwise.
        Default:
        true
